  <brief_title>Effect of Partial Sleep Deprivation on Cognition and Cytokines in Individuals With Major Depression</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 4 Study on the Effect of Partial Sleep Deprivation on Cognition and the IL-6-gp130-System in Individuals With Major Depression</official_title>
